{"tid":275817,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大阪環球影城任天堂區動工！機動設施設計曝光","createTime":"2017-06-08T10:31:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-08T11:53:11.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"49d7076a53e8fc2d7dbd686de5ce893216f3c6ca","tid":275817,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T10:31:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nUu5tUsD9VE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DnUu5tUsD9VE&d=9QbquKIHcXcapsTpPLjnchxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=b0f47384\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nUu5tUsD9VE</a><br />\n日本位於大阪的環球影城真是怎樣都不會悶，全球最大的 Minion Park 今年 4 月才剛剛開幕，而任天堂園區也終於在今天開始動工了！近日工作人員加緊建造『SUPER NINTENDO WORLD』建設着工式所用到的舞臺，經典的紅磚、綠色水管、問號磚一樣不少，就連噴出來的紙碎都竟然是金幣以及蘑菇，Mario 都到場坐鎮！<br />\n<br />\n大阪 USJ 的任天堂園區於 2017 年 6 月 8 日進行動工式，投資 600 億円，目標在 2020 年東京奧運會前開幕。USJ 情報局 Twitter 就放出多張任天堂園區的工地圖以及機動設施設計圖。雖然不知真假，但看見就覺得興奮，大家一起期待吧！<br />\n<a href=\"http://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1831519?=v\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F1831519%3F%3Dv&d=9QbquKIHcXcapsTpPLjnchxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=fa2d5dd6\" target=\"_blank\">http://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1831519?=v</a>"},{"pid":"4d13c04bbcd3afb216c5d567f95d1a13e5a796b5","tid":275817,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T10:44:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0685f8b6ae8327738e8d5007bfa1496f21430d96","tid":275817,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T11:13:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa4c19f4f75d81033f26991e9db9ef523d4a860d","tid":275817,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T11